## Configure Uno Platform Project for UI Tests (XML)

```xml
<PropertyGroup Condition="'$(Configuration)'=='Debug' or '$(IsUiAutomationMappingEnabled)'=='True'">
		<IsUiAutomationMappingEnabled>True</IsUiAutomationMappingEnabled>
		<DefineConstants>$(DefineConstants);USE_UITESTS</DefineConstants>
	</PropertyGroup>
```

## Configure WebAssembly Testing with Selenium

```csharp
using Uno.UITest.Selenium;
using System;

// Basic configuration
var app = Uno.UITest.Selenium.ConfigureApp
    .WebAssembly
    .Uri(new Uri("http://localhost:54490/"))
    .UsingBrowser("Chrome")
    .Headless(true)
    .WindowSize(1024, 768)
    .StartApp();

// Advanced configuration with custom driver path
var configurator = Uno.UITest.Selenium.ConfigureApp
    .WebAssembly
    .Uri(new Uri("http://localhost:8080/"))
    .UsingBrowser("Edge")
    .Headless(false)
    .DriverPath("/path/to/chromedriver")
    .BrowserPath("/path/to/chrome")
    .WindowSize(1920, 1080)
    .ScreenShotsPath("./screenshots")
    .SeleniumArgument("--remote-debugging-port=9222")
    .DetectDockerEnvironment(true);

var app = configurator.StartApp();

// Environment variable overrides
// UNO_UITEST_TARGETURI - Override target URI
// UNO_UITEST_BROWSER - Override browser (CHROME or EDGE)
// UNO_UITEST_DRIVER_PATH - Override driver path
// UNO_UITEST_SCREENSHOT_PATH - Override screenshot path

```

